      "term": "samnite",
      "kind": "word",
      "cefrLevel": "null",
      "senses": [
        {
          "pos": "noun",
          "definition": "an ancient Oscan-speaking people who lived in Samnium in southern Italy",
          "examples": [
            "The Samnites fought a long war with Rome in early Italian history.",
            "Ancient Samnite culture is known from inscriptions and fortifications."
